snippet.title: Powerful Wind, Slicked-back Cabbages · Free Game · Showcase
snippet.description:
Link to play: https://async-fish.itch.io/powerful-wind-slicked-back-cabbages
Powerful Wind, Slicked-back Cabbages is a cool, one-tap rhythm game where you slice cabbages while listening to the popular Japanese song "Powerful Wind, Slicked-back Hair" by Yukopi. Good luck!

Credits:

• Yukopi: https://www.youtube.com/@yukopi_
• Fish: https://async-fish.itch.io/
